{
  "spec": {
    "title": "Largest Contentful Paint",
    "url": "https://w3c.github.io/largest-contentful-paint/"
  },
  "algorithms": [
    {
      "name": "LargestContentfulPaint element",
      "html": "",
      "rationale": ".algorithm",
      "steps": [
        {
          "html": "<p>If <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#this\" id=\"ref-for-this⑥\">this</a>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/largest-contentful-paint/#largestcontentfulpaint-element\" id=\"ref-for-largestcontentfulpaint-element\">element</a> is not <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/paint-timing/#exposed-for-paint-timing\" id=\"ref-for-exposed-for-paint-timing\">exposed for paint timing</a> given null, return null.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Return <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#this\" id=\"ref-for-this⑦\">this</a>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/largest-contentful-paint/#largestcontentfulpaint-element\" id=\"ref-for-largestcontentfulpaint-element①\">element</a>.</p>"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "report largest contentful paint",
      "href": "https://w3c.github.io/largest-contentful-paint/#report-largest-contentful-paint",
      "html": "When asked to <dfn class=\"dfn-paneled has-dfn-panel\" data-dfn-type=\"dfn\" data-export=\"\" id=\"report-largest-contentful-paint\" role=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" tabindex=\"0\">report largest contentful paint</dfn> given a <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#document\" id=\"ref-for-document②\">Document</a></code> <var>document</var>, a <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/paint-timing/#paint-timing-info\" id=\"ref-for-paint-timing-info①\">paint timing info</a> <var>paintTimingInfo</var>, an <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://infra.spec.whatwg.org/#ordered-set\" id=\"ref-for-ordered-set\">ordered set</a> of <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/paint-timing/#pending-image-record\" id=\"ref-for-pending-image-record\">pending image records</a> <var>paintedImages</var>, and an <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://infra.spec.whatwg.org/#ordered-set\" id=\"ref-for-ordered-set①\">ordered set</a> of <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org#concept-element\" id=\"ref-for-concept-element①\">elements</a> <var>paintedTextNodes</var>, perform the following steps:",
      "rationale": ".algorithm",
      "steps": [
        {
          "html": "<p>Let <var>window</var> be <var>document</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/webappapis.html#concept-relevant-global\" id=\"ref-for-concept-relevant-global②\">relevant global object</a>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>If either of <var>window</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/largest-contentful-paint/#has-dispatched-scroll-event\" id=\"ref-for-has-dispatched-scroll-event①\">has dispatched scroll event</a> or <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/event-timing#has-dispatched-input-event\" id=\"ref-for-has-dispatched-input-event\">has dispatched input event</a> is true, return.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Let <var>newCandidate</var> be the result of <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/largest-contentful-paint/#compute-a-new-largest-contentful-paint-candidate\" id=\"ref-for-compute-a-new-largest-contentful-paint-candidate\">computing a new largest contentful paint candidate</a> given <var>document</var>, <var>paintedImages</var>, <var>paintedTextNodes</var>, and <var>document</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/largest-contentful-paint/#current-largest-contentful-paint-candidate\" id=\"ref-for-current-largest-contentful-paint-candidate\">current largest contentful paint candidate</a>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>If <var>newCandidate</var> is null, return.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Set <var>document</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/largest-contentful-paint/#current-largest-contentful-paint-candidate\" id=\"ref-for-current-largest-contentful-paint-candidate①\">current largest contentful paint candidate</a> to <var>newCandidate</var>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Let <var>entry</var> be the result of <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/largest-contentful-paint/#create-a-largestcontentfulpaint-entry\" id=\"ref-for-create-a-largestcontentfulpaint-entry\">creating a LargestContentfulPaint entry</a> with <var>newCandidate</var>, <var>paintTimingInfo</var>, and <var>document</var>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p><a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/performance-timeline/#dfn-queue-a-performanceentry\" id=\"ref-for-dfn-queue-a-performanceentry\">Queue the PerformanceEntry</a> <var>entry</var>.</p>"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "compute a new largest contentful paint candidate",
      "href": "https://w3c.github.io/largest-contentful-paint/#compute-a-new-largest-contentful-paint-candidate",
      "html": "To <dfn class=\"dfn-paneled has-dfn-panel\" data-dfn-type=\"dfn\" data-export=\"\" id=\"compute-a-new-largest-contentful-paint-candidate\" role=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" tabindex=\"0\">compute a new largest contentful paint candidate</dfn>, given a <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#document\" id=\"ref-for-document③\">Document</a></code> <var>document</var>, an <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://infra.spec.whatwg.org/#ordered-set\" id=\"ref-for-ordered-set②\">ordered set</a> of <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/paint-timing/#pending-image-record\" id=\"ref-for-pending-image-record①\">pending image records</a> <var>paintedImages</var>, an <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://infra.spec.whatwg.org/#ordered-set\" id=\"ref-for-ordered-set③\">ordered set</a> of <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org#concept-element\" id=\"ref-for-concept-element②\">elements</a> <var>paintedTextNodes</var>, and a <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/largest-contentful-paint/#largest-contentful-paint-candidate\" id=\"ref-for-largest-contentful-paint-candidate②\">largest contentful paint candidate</a> or null <var>currentCandidate</var>, perform the following steps. They return a <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/largest-contentful-paint/#largest-contentful-paint-candidate\" id=\"ref-for-largest-contentful-paint-candidate③\">largest contentful paint candidate</a> or null.",
      "rationale": ".algorithm",
      "steps": [
        {
          "html": "<p>Let <var>currentSize</var> be <var>currentCandidate</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/largest-contentful-paint/#largest-contentful-paint-candidate-size\" id=\"ref-for-largest-contentful-paint-candidate-size\">size</a> if <var>currentCandidate</var> is not null or 0 otherwise.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Let <var>largestSize</var> be <var>currentSize</var>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Let <var>newCandidate</var> be null.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://infra.spec.whatwg.org/#list-iterate\" id=\"ref-for-list-iterate\">For each</a> <var>record</var> of <var>paintedImages</var>:",
          "rationale": "let",
          "steps": [
            {
              "html": "<p>Let <var>imageElement</var> be <var>record</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/paint-timing/#pending-image-record-element\" id=\"ref-for-pending-image-record-element\">element</a>.</p>"
            },
            {
              "html": "<p>If <var>imageElement</var> is not <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/paint-timing/#exposed-for-paint-timing\" id=\"ref-for-exposed-for-paint-timing①\">exposed for paint timing</a>, given <var>document</var>, continue.</p>"
            },
            {
              "html": "<p>Let <var>intersectionRect</var> be the value returned by the intersection rect algorithm using <var>imageElement</var> as the target and viewport as the root.</p>"
            },
            {
              "html": "<p>Let <var>result</var> be the <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/largest-contentful-paint/#effective-visual-size\" id=\"ref-for-effective-visual-size\">effective visual size</a> of <var>imageElement</var> given <var>intersectionRect</var> and <var>record</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/paint-timing/#pending-image-record-request\" id=\"ref-for-pending-image-record-request\">request</a>.</p>"
            },
            {
              "html": "<p>If <var>result</var> is null, continue.</p>"
            },
            {
              "html": "<p>If <var>result</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/largest-contentful-paint/#effective-visual-size-result-size\" id=\"ref-for-effective-visual-size-result-size\">size</a> is less than or equal to <var>largestSize</var>, continue.</p>"
            },
            {
              "html": "<p>Set <var>largestSize</var> to <var>result</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/largest-contentful-paint/#effective-visual-size-result-size\" id=\"ref-for-effective-visual-size-result-size①\">size</a>.</p>"
            },
            {
              "html": "<p>Set <var>newCandidate</var> to be a new <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/largest-contentful-paint/#largest-contentful-paint-candidate\" id=\"ref-for-largest-contentful-paint-candidate④\">largest contentful paint candidate</a> with the following values:</p>",
              "ignored": [
                "element set to imageElement. size set to result’s size. width set to result’s width. height set to result’s height. request set to record’s request. loadTime set to record’s loadTime."
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "html": "<a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://infra.spec.whatwg.org/#list-iterate\" id=\"ref-for-list-iterate①\">For each</a> <var>textNode</var> of <var>paintedTextNodes</var>,",
          "rationale": "if",
          "steps": [
            {
              "html": "<p>If <var>textNode</var> is not <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/paint-timing/#exposed-for-paint-timing\" id=\"ref-for-exposed-for-paint-timing②\">exposed for paint timing</a>, given <var>document</var>, continue.</p>"
            },
            {
              "html": "If <var>textNode</var> has <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-color-4/#alpha-channel\" id=\"ref-for-alpha-channel\">alpha channel</a> value &lt;=0 or <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-color-3/#opacity\" id=\"ref-for-opacity\">opacity</a> value &lt;=0:",
              "rationale": "if",
              "steps": [
                {
                  "html": "<p>If <var>textNode</var>’s <a class=\"css\" data-link-type=\"property\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-text-decor-4/#propdef-text-shadow\" id=\"ref-for-propdef-text-shadow\">text-shadow</a> value is none, <var>textNode</var>’s <a class=\"css property\" data-link-type=\"property\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/fill-stroke-3/#propdef-stroke-color\" id=\"ref-for-propdef-stroke-color\">stroke-color</a> value is <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-color-3/#transparent\" id=\"ref-for-transparent\">transparent</a> and <var>textNode</var>’s <a class=\"css property\" data-link-type=\"property\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/fill-stroke-3/#propdef-stroke-image\" id=\"ref-for-propdef-stroke-image\">stroke-image</a> value is none, continue.</p>"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "html": "<p>Let <var>intersectionRect</var> be the union of the border boxes of all <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#text\" id=\"ref-for-text\">Text</a></code> <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#concept-node\" id=\"ref-for-concept-node\">nodes</a> in <var>textNode</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/paint-timing/#set-of-owned-text-nodes\" id=\"ref-for-set-of-owned-text-nodes\">set of owned text nodes</a>, intersected with the visual viewport.</p>"
            },
            {
              "html": "<p>Let <var>result</var> be the <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/largest-contentful-paint/#effective-visual-size\" id=\"ref-for-effective-visual-size①\">effective visual size</a> of <var>textNode</var> given <var>intersectionRect</var> and null.</p>"
            },
            {
              "html": "<p>If <var>result</var> is null, continue.</p>"
            },
            {
              "html": "<p>If <var>result</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/largest-contentful-paint/#effective-visual-size-result-size\" id=\"ref-for-effective-visual-size-result-size③\">size</a> is less than or equal to <var>largestSize</var>, continue.</p>"
            },
            {
              "html": "<p>Set <var>largestSize</var> to <var>result</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/largest-contentful-paint/#effective-visual-size-result-size\" id=\"ref-for-effective-visual-size-result-size④\">size</a>.</p>"
            },
            {
              "html": "<p>Set <var>newCandidate</var> to be a new <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/largest-contentful-paint/#largest-contentful-paint-candidate\" id=\"ref-for-largest-contentful-paint-candidate⑤\">largest contentful paint candidate</a> with the following values:</p>",
              "ignored": [
                "element set to textNode. size set to result’s size. width set to result’s width. height set to result’s height. request set to null. loadTime set to 0."
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "html": "If <var>newCandidate</var> is not null and <var>currentSize</var> is greater than 0:",
          "rationale": "if",
          "steps": [
            {
              "html": "<p>If <var>newCandidate</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/largest-contentful-paint/#largest-contentful-paint-candidate-width\" id=\"ref-for-largest-contentful-paint-candidate-width②\">width</a> minus <var>currentCandidate</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/largest-contentful-paint/#largest-contentful-paint-candidate-width\" id=\"ref-for-largest-contentful-paint-candidate-width③\">width</a> is less than or equal to 3, and <var>newCandidate</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/largest-contentful-paint/#largest-contentful-paint-candidate-height\" id=\"ref-for-largest-contentful-paint-candidate-height②\">height</a> minus <var>currentCandidate</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/largest-contentful-paint/#largest-contentful-paint-candidate-height\" id=\"ref-for-largest-contentful-paint-candidate-height③\">height</a> is less than or equal to 3, return null.</p>"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Return <var>newCandidate</var>.</p>"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "LargestContentfulPaint effective-visual-size",
      "href": "https://w3c.github.io/largest-contentful-paint/#effective-visual-size-result",
      "html": "An <dfn class=\"dfn-paneled has-dfn-panel\" data-dfn-type=\"dfn\" data-noexport=\"\" id=\"effective-visual-size-result\" role=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" tabindex=\"0\">effective visual size result</dfn>, which is a <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://infra.spec.whatwg.org/#struct\" id=\"ref-for-struct①\">struct</a> with items <dfn class=\"dfn-paneled has-dfn-panel\" data-dfn-for=\"effective visual size result\" data-dfn-type=\"dfn\" data-noexport=\"\" id=\"effective-visual-size-result-size\" role=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" tabindex=\"0\">size</dfn> (a <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-values-4/#number\" id=\"ref-for-number④\">number</a>), <dfn class=\"dfn-paneled has-dfn-panel\" data-dfn-for=\"effective visual size result\" data-dfn-type=\"dfn\" data-noexport=\"\" id=\"effective-visual-size-result-width\" role=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" tabindex=\"0\">width</dfn> (a <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-values-4/#number\" id=\"ref-for-number⑤\">number</a>), and <dfn class=\"dfn-paneled has-dfn-panel\" data-dfn-for=\"effective visual size result\" data-dfn-type=\"dfn\" data-noexport=\"\" id=\"effective-visual-size-result-height\" role=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" tabindex=\"0\">height</dfn> (a <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-values-4/#number\" id=\"ref-for-number⑥\">number</a>), representing the effective visual size, width, and height to report for Largest Contentful Paint, in pixels; or null if the element should not be an LCP candidate.",
      "rationale": ".algorithm",
      "steps": [
        {
          "html": "<p>Let <var>width</var> be <var>intersectionRect</var>’s <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/geometry-1/#dom-domrectreadonly-width\" id=\"ref-for-dom-domrectreadonly-width\">width</a></code>, rounded up to the nearest integer.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Let <var>height</var> be <var>intersectionRect</var>’s <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/geometry-1/#dom-domrectreadonly-height\" id=\"ref-for-dom-domrectreadonly-height\">height</a></code>, rounded up to the nearest integer.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Let <var>size</var> be <code class=\"highlight\"><var>width</var> <c- o=\"\">*</c-> <var>height</var></code>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Let <var>root</var> be <var>document</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/document-sequences.html#concept-document-bc\" id=\"ref-for-concept-document-bc\">browsing context</a>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/document-sequences.html#top-level-browsing-context\" id=\"ref-for-top-level-browsing-context\">top-level browsing context</a>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/document-sequences.html#nav-document\" id=\"ref-for-nav-document\">active document</a>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Let <var>rootWidth</var> be <var>root</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/cssom-view/#visual-viewport\" id=\"ref-for-visual-viewport\">visual viewport</a>’s width, excluding any scrollbars.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Let <var>rootHeight</var> be <var>root</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/cssom-view/#visual-viewport\" id=\"ref-for-visual-viewport①\">visual viewport</a>’s height, excluding any scrollbars.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>If <var>size</var> is equal to <var>rootWidth</var> times <var>rootHeight</var>, return null.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "If <var>imageRequest</var> is not null, run the following steps to adjust for image position and upscaling:",
          "rationale": "if",
          "steps": [
            {
              "html": "<p>If <var>imageRequest</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://fetch.spec.whatwg.org/#concept-response\" id=\"ref-for-concept-response\">response</a>’s content length in bytes is less than <var>size</var> * 0.004, then return null.</p>"
            },
            {
              "html": "<p>Let <var>concreteDimensions</var> be <var>imageRequest</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-images-3/#concrete-object-size\" id=\"ref-for-concrete-object-size\">concrete object size</a> within <var>element</var>.</p>"
            },
            {
              "html": "<p>Let <var>visibleDimensions</var> be <var>concreteDimensions</var>, adjusted for positioning by <a class=\"css property\" data-link-type=\"property\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-images-3/#propdef-object-position\" id=\"ref-for-propdef-object-position\">object-position</a> or <a class=\"css property\" data-link-type=\"property\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-backgrounds-3/#propdef-background-position\" id=\"ref-for-propdef-background-position\">background-position</a> and <var>element</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-box-4/#content-box\" id=\"ref-for-content-box\">content box</a>.</p>"
            },
            {
              "html": "<p>Let <var>clientContentRect</var> be the smallest <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/geometry-1/#domrectreadonly\" id=\"ref-for-domrectreadonly②\">DOMRectReadOnly</a></code> containing <var>visibleDimensions</var> with <var>element</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://streams.spec.whatwg.org/#generictransformstream-transform\" id=\"ref-for-generictransformstream-transform\">transforms</a> applied.</p>"
            },
            {
              "html": "<p>Let <var>intersectingClientContentRect</var> be the intersection of <var>clientContentRect</var> with <var>intersectionRect</var>.</p>"
            },
            {
              "html": "<p>Set <var>width</var> to <var>intersectingClientContentRect</var>’s <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/geometry-1/#dom-domrectreadonly-width\" id=\"ref-for-dom-domrectreadonly-width①\">width</a></code>, rounded up to the nearest integer.</p>"
            },
            {
              "html": "<p>Set <var>height</var> to <var>intersectingClientContentRect</var>’s <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/geometry-1/#dom-domrectreadonly-height\" id=\"ref-for-dom-domrectreadonly-height①\">height</a></code>, rounded up to the nearest integer.</p>"
            },
            {
              "html": "<p>Set <var>size</var> to <code class=\"highlight\"><var>width</var> <c- o=\"\">*</c-> <var>height</var></code>.</p>"
            },
            {
              "html": "<p>Let <var>naturalArea</var> be <code class=\"highlight\"><var>imageRequest</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-images-3/#natural-width\" id=\"ref-for-natural-width\">natural width</a> <c- o=\"\">*</c-> <var>imageRequest</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-images-3/#natural-height\" id=\"ref-for-natural-height\">natural height</a></code>.</p>"
            },
            {
              "html": "<p>If <var>naturalArea</var> is 0, then return null.</p>"
            },
            {
              "html": "<p>Let <var>boundingClientArea</var> be <code class=\"highlight\"><var>clientContentRect</var>’s <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/geometry-1/#dom-domrectreadonly-width\" id=\"ref-for-dom-domrectreadonly-width②\">width</a></code> <c- o=\"\">*</c-> <var>clientContentRect</var>’s <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/geometry-1/#dom-domrectreadonly-height\" id=\"ref-for-dom-domrectreadonly-height②\">height</a></code></code>.</p>"
            },
            {
              "html": "<p>Let <var>scaleFactor</var> be <code class=\"highlight\"><var>boundingClientArea</var> <c- o=\"\">/</c-> <var>naturalArea</var></code>.</p>"
            },
            {
              "html": "<p>If <var>scaleFactor</var> is greater than 1, then divide <var>size</var> by <var>scaleFactor</var>.</p>"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Return an <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/largest-contentful-paint/#effective-visual-size-result\" id=\"ref-for-effective-visual-size-result\">effective visual size result</a> with <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/largest-contentful-paint/#effective-visual-size-result-size\" id=\"ref-for-effective-visual-size-result-size⑥\">size</a> set to <var>size</var>, <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/largest-contentful-paint/#effective-visual-size-result-width\" id=\"ref-for-effective-visual-size-result-width②\">width</a> set to <var>width</var>, and <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/largest-contentful-paint/#effective-visual-size-result-height\" id=\"ref-for-effective-visual-size-result-height②\">height</a> set to <var>height</var>.</p>"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "LargestContentfulPaint create-entry",
      "html": "A <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/largest-contentful-paint/#largestcontentfulpaint\" id=\"ref-for-largestcontentfulpaint④\">LargestContentfulPaint</a></code>",
      "rationale": ".algorithm",
      "steps": [
        {
          "html": "<p>Let <var>url</var> be the empty string.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>If <var>candidate</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/largest-contentful-paint/#largest-contentful-paint-candidate-request\" id=\"ref-for-largest-contentful-paint-candidate-request②\">request</a> is not null, set <var>url</var> to be <var>candidate</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/largest-contentful-paint/#largest-contentful-paint-candidate-request\" id=\"ref-for-largest-contentful-paint-candidate-request③\">request</a>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://fetch.spec.whatwg.org/#dom-request-url\" id=\"ref-for-dom-request-url\">request URL</a>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Let <var>entry</var> be a new <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/largest-contentful-paint/#largestcontentfulpaint\" id=\"ref-for-largestcontentfulpaint⑤\">LargestContentfulPaint</a></code> entry with <var>document</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/webappapis.html#concept-relevant-realm\" id=\"ref-for-concept-relevant-realm\">relevant realm</a>, whose <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/paint-timing/#paint-timing-info\" id=\"ref-for-paint-timing-info③\">paint timing info</a> is <var>paintTimingInfo</var>, with its</p>\n        <ul>\n         <li data-md=\"\">\n          <p><code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/largest-contentful-paint/#dom-largestcontentfulpaint-size\" id=\"ref-for-dom-largestcontentfulpaint-size①\">size</a></code> set to <var>candidate</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/largest-contentful-paint/#largest-contentful-paint-candidate-size\" id=\"ref-for-largest-contentful-paint-candidate-size③\">size</a>,</p>\n         </li><li data-md=\"\">\n          <p><code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/largest-contentful-paint/#dom-largestcontentfulpaint-url\" id=\"ref-for-dom-largestcontentfulpaint-url①\">url</a></code> set to <var>url</var>,</p>\n         </li><li data-md=\"\">\n          <p><code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/largest-contentful-paint/#dom-largestcontentfulpaint-id\" id=\"ref-for-dom-largestcontentfulpaint-id①\">id</a></code> set to <var>candidate</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/largest-contentful-paint/#largest-contentful-paint-candidate-element\" id=\"ref-for-largest-contentful-paint-candidate-element③\">element</a>’s <a class=\"idl-code\" data-link-type=\"attribute\" href=\"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org#dom-element-id\" id=\"ref-for-dom-element-id\">element id</a>,</p>\n         </li><li data-md=\"\">\n          <p><code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/largest-contentful-paint/#dom-largestcontentfulpaint-loadtime\" id=\"ref-for-dom-largestcontentfulpaint-loadtime①\">loadTime</a></code> set to <var>candidate</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/largest-contentful-paint/#largest-contentful-paint-candidate-loadtime\" id=\"ref-for-largest-contentful-paint-candidate-loadtime②\">loadTime</a>,</p>\n         </li><li data-md=\"\">\n          <p>and <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/largest-contentful-paint/#dom-largestcontentfulpaint-element\" id=\"ref-for-dom-largestcontentfulpaint-element②\">element</a></code> set to <var>candidate</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/largest-contentful-paint/#largest-contentful-paint-candidate-element\" id=\"ref-for-largest-contentful-paint-candidate-element④\">element</a>.</p>\n        </li></ul>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Return <var>entry</var>.</p>"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}